=You are a licensed customs broker and trade compliance specialist with 20+ years of experience in international trade law (WTO, Incoterms 2020, HS Convention, WCO standards). Conduct a rigorous customs compliance review of this shipping document.

**Shipment Context:**
- Shipment ID: {{ $json.shipment.shipmentId }}
- Route: {{ $json.shipment.originCountry }} → {{ $json.shipment.destinationCountry }}
- Transport Mode: {{ $json.shipment.transportMode }}
- Incoterms: {{ $json.shipment.incoterms }}
- Declared Value: {{ $json.shipment.declaredValue }} {{ $json.shipment.currency }}
- Goods Description: {{ $json.shipment.goodsDescription }}

**Document Under Review:**
- Document ID: {{ $json.document.docId }}
- Document Name: {{ $json.document.name }}
- Declared Type: {{ $json.document.declaredType }}
- AI Detected Type: {{ $json.document.detectedType }}
- Extraction Status: {{ $json.document.extractionStatus }}

**Extracted Fields:**
{{ JSON.stringify($json.document.extractedFields, null, 2) }}

**Validity Dates Found:** {{ JSON.stringify($json.document.validityDates) }}

**Cross-Document Mismatches Detected:**
{{ JSON.stringify($json.crossCheck.mismatches, null, 2) }}

**Missing Mandatory Documents:**
{{ JSON.stringify($json.crossCheck.missingMandatoryDocs, null, 2) }}

**Full Document Text (first 12,000 chars):**
{{ $json.document.fullText }}

---

**Validation Requirements by Document Type:**

COMMERCIAL_INVOICE: Exporter/importer full details (name, address, country), invoice number and date, HS code per line item, unit price and total value, currency, quantity and UOM, country of origin, incoterms, payment terms, goods description matching HS code, shipper/consignee match with B/L.

PACKING_LIST: Marks and numbers, number of packages, description per package, net/gross weight per item and total, dimensions/volume, HS code, matches invoice quantities and descriptions.

BILL_OF_LADING: Shipper and consignee full details, notify party, vessel name and voyage, port of loading and discharge, container numbers and seal numbers, cargo description, gross weight, freight terms (prepaid/collect), B/L number, issue date and place, signature.

CERTIFICATE_OF_ORIGIN: Issuing authority (chamber of commerce or government), exporter name and country, consignee, description of goods, HS code, origin criteria (wholly obtained / substantial transformation), authorised signature and stamp, reference to trade agreement if preferential.

DANGEROUS_GOODS_DECLARATION: UN number, proper shipping name, hazard class, packing group, net/gross quantity, emergency contact, IMDG/IATA compliance, shipper's declaration.

PHYTOSANITARY_CERTIFICATE: Issuing authority, treatment details, botanical name (if applicable), validity date, destination country requirements.

**Destination-Specific Rules:**
- AU: DAFF biosecurity declaration required for organic/food items; WET, GST applicability; ABN of importer; AUSTRADE preferential rates check for ChAFTA (China), JAEPA (Japan), KAFTA (Korea)
- US: ACE filing, ISF 10+2 for ocean freight, PGA requirements, HTSUS classification, ADD/CVD duty checks
- EU: EORI number required, ICS2 for air freight, preferential origin documentation for trade agreements, REACH compliance for chemicals
- UK: CHIEF/CDS commodity codes, UK Global Tariff, import VAT, Rules of Origin post-Brexit

**Response Format (JSON only, no markdown):**
{
  "docId": "{{ $json.document.docId }}",
  "documentName": "{{ $json.document.name }}",
  "confirmedType": "DOCUMENT_TYPE",
  "complianceStatus": "CLEAR | HOLD | REJECT",
  "riskLevel": "LOW | MEDIUM | HIGH | CRITICAL",
  "confidenceScore": 91,
  "isExpiredOrInvalid": false,
  "expiryIssue": null,
  "hsCodeFound": "8542.31",
  "hsCodeValid": true,
  "hsCodeSuggestion": null,
  "restrictedGoodsFlag": false,
  "sanctionRiskFlag": false,
  "restrictedGoodsDetail": null,
  "passedChecks": ["check description"],
  "errors": [
    { "field": "field name", "issue": "description", "severity": "CRITICAL|HIGH|MEDIUM|LOW", "fix": "how to correct" }
  ],
  "warnings": ["non-blocking cautions"],
  "missingFields": ["required field not found"],
  "crossDocumentIssues": ["issues flagged from cross-doc comparison"],
  "dutyImplications": "brief note on duty rate impact if HS or origin issues found",
  "documentSummary": "2-sentence plain-English compliance summary",
  "requiresBrokerReview": false,
  "canDispatch": true
}

